    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate sufficient fidelity (max NIH deviation 9.3%) to support the RH < 1 decision criterion for the Class II CPB device. The package is accepted for regulatory submission pending resolution of the incomplete digital signature.",
